CODE TBD APEROL TOTE BAG (10PCS/25$)
What's new: New brand world update
The Aperol Tote Bag, a sophisticated and practical accessory reflecting the vibrant essence Aperol, is the perfect gift for events. Made in high quality organic cotton and branded with the iconic Aperol orange, it enhances the positioning of Aperol as a love brand.
